pticism-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%20threatens%20to%20automate%3C%2Fa%3E%20some%20of%20the%20work%20agencies%20do%2C%20and%20many%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20wondering%20what%20Vaynerchuk's%20next%20big%20act%20will%20be.%20CMOs%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20be%20convinced%20to%20embrace%20social%20media%2C%20and%20many%20have%20bypassed%20agencies%20like%20VaynerX%20altogether%20to%20take%20that%20work%20in-house.%20Firms%20like%20VaynerX%20have%20had%20to%20diversify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20creative%20agencies%20are%20shrinking%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0holding%20companies%20downsize%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Farmer%2C%20a%20consultant%20to%20ad%20agencies%20and%20marketers.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20healthy%20business.%20Nobody%20knows%20what%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaynerchuk%20still%20evangelizes%20to%20CMOs%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20social%20media%20marketing.%20But%20his%20passions%20have%20expanded%20to%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fwhere-to-buy-ray-ban-meta-glasses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%20Ray-Bans%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Vaynerchuk%20is%20an%20investor%20in%20Meta)%2C%20which%20he%20thinks%20could%20replace%20the%20mobile%20phone.%20He's%20big%20on%20live%20social%20shopping%2C%20which%20he%20predicts%20will%20blow%20up%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20styled%20himself%20as%20something%20of%20an%20AI%20guru.%20Vaynerchuk's%20stance%20is%20that%20business%20leaders%20should%20find%20a%20middle%20ground%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20new%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20demonize%20it%2C%20like%2C%20'We'll%20never%20do%20AI%3B%20that's%20bad%20for%20humanity%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOr%20the%20other%20way%3A%20'Oh%20great%2C%20we%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20anything%20else%3B%20AI%20will%20take%20care%20of%20it.'%20So%2C%20let's%20not%20get%20too%20high%20on%20it.%20Let's%20not%20get%20too%20low%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaynerchuk%20urges%20clients%20to%20see%20AI's%20potential%20beyond%20just%20cost%20savings.%20%26quot%3BWe%20talk%20about%20it%20from%20internal%20and%20external%20efficiencies%20of%20course%2C%20but%20clients%20are%20starting%20to%20understand%20the%20big%20game%2C%20which%20is%2C%20'How%20do%20you%20earn%20views%20in%20social%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they're%20agnostic%2C%20whether%20that's%20an%20AI%20piece%20of%20creative%20or%20a%20human%20piece%20of%20creative.%20They%20just%20want%20to%20get%20the%20awareness%20and%20the%20consideration%20and%20the%20relevancy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20marketing%20is%20still%20central%20to%20the%20company's%20identity.%20One%20of%20Vaynerchuk's%20coups%20in%202023%20was%20helping%20PepsiCo%20jump-start%20sales%20for%20Mug%20Root%20Beer%20by%20suggesting%20new%20uses%20for%20the%2080-plus-year-old%20brand%2C%20like%20using%20it%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmugrootbeer%2Freel%2FC3tJw_MvtNc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eramen%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Boba%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Lyons%2C%20CMO%20of%20PepsiCo's%20North%20American%20beverage%20business%2C%20said%20rather%20than%20going%20the%20traditional%20marketing%20route%20of%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20time%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20single%20message%2C%20VaynerX's%20media%20agency%2C%20VaynerMedia%2C%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20waited%20to%20see%20which%20ones%20took%20off%20before%20deciding%20which%20message%20to%20put%20dollars%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20I%20love%20most%20about%20Vayner%20is%20that%20they're%20social-first%2C%20which%20means%20they%20understand%20what%20happens%20in%20culture%20very%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Lyons%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20shot%20Super%20Bowl%20ads%20in%20the%20past%20for%20us.%20But%20they're%20at%20their%20best%20when%20they'r