%20ornaments%20were%20seized%20as%20symbols%20of%20the%20regime's%20falL.%20Storerooms%20were%20ransacked%20for%20any%20valuable%20remnants%20of%20the%20fallen%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20scene%20of%20rebellion%20mirrored%20the%20events%20in%20Bangladesh%20in%20August.%20When%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20left%20Dhaka%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasinas-sarees-paintings-at-palace-stolen-by-mob-after-she-flees-6269464%C2%A0%5C%22%3Eprotesters%20stormed%20her%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ganabhaban%2C%20looting%20food%2C%20kitchen%20items%20and%20furniture.%20Personal%20belongings%2C%20including%20sarees%2C%20a%20Dior%20suitcase%20and%20even%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20Hilsa%20fish%2C%20Bangladesh's%20national%20symbol%2C%20were%20taken%20or%20destroyed.%20A%20viral%20image%20showed%20a%20man%20lounging%20on%20Hasina's%20bed%2C%20declaring%2C%20the%20building%20%26quot%3Bunder%20our%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20Sunday%2C%20the%20US%20launched%20a%20series%20of%20airstrikes%20targeting%20Islamic%20State%20(ISIS)%20positions%20in%20Syria%2C%20following%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Syrian%20government.%20Following%20the%20capture%20of%20Damascus%2C%20reports%20confirmed%20that%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20along%20with%20his%20family%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbashar-al-assad-gone-to-russia-us-strikes-isis-camps-inside-syria-7204421%C2%A0%5C%22%3Efled%20to%20Moscow%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20was%20granted%20asylum%20by%20the%20Russian%20government.%20It%20marked%20an%20end%20to%20the%20Assad%20family's%20six-decade%20rule%20over%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%20leader%20Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Jolani%20also%20addressed%20a%20crowd%20in%20Damascus%20on%20Sunday.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20new%20history%2C%20my%20brothers%2C%20is%20being%20written%20in%20the%20entire%20region%20af