20submit%20your%20application%2C%20and%20there's%20just%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1ef5e75-fb2e-44c5-b2ff-9b2c828deb4d%5C%22%3ECompeting%20against%20laid-off%20coders%20with%20more%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFacing%20low%20response%20rates%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghost-jobs-why-some-companies-dont-respond-to-applications-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eghost%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20postings%2C%20software%20engineers%20fresh%20out%20of%20school%20are%20also%20having%20to%20compete%20with%20their%20more%20experienced%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20companies%20continuing%20to%20trim%20their%20staff%2C%20the%20tech%20sector%20has%20also%20faced%20two%20years%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-explain-the-tech-layoffs-mark-zuckeberg-sundar-pichai-2024-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrutal%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202022%2C%20over%20165%2C000%20employees%20were%20cut%20from%20a%20thousand%20tech%20companies%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flayoffs.fyi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELayoffs.fyi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20website%20tracking%20tech%20layoffs.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20number%20of%20layoffs%20increased%20to%20over%20264%2C000.%20So%20far%20in%202024%2C%20nearly%20150%2C000%20employees%20have%20been%20cut%20from%20over%20520%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20already%20established%20tech%20workers%20cut%20loose%20into%20the%20job%20market%2C%20new%20graduates%20are%20facing%20increased%20competition%20for%20fewer%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmos%20Ker%2C%20a%20recent%20graduate%20from%20New%20York%20University%2C%20said%20that%20although%20sub-industries%20within%20computer%20science%2C%20like%20AI%20and%20LLMs%2C%20are%20booming%20as%20Big%20Tech%20invests%20heavily%2C%20these%20fields%20often%20require%20a%20higher