0hiring%2C%20so%20I%20jumped%20out%20of%20bed%20and%20did%20an%20interview%2C%20but%20I%20could%20hardly%20pay%20attention.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20Brazil%20for%20a%20week%20to%20be%20close%20to%20my%20childhood%20friends.%20For%20those%20of%20us%20in%20tech%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20world%20was%20falling%20apart%2C%20but%20I'm%20from%20an%20island%20in%20the%20south%20of%20Brazil%2C%20and%20being%20there%20helped%20me%20keep%20that%20in%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20moving%20to%20Miami%2C%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20friends%20had%20moved%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20Climate%20tech%20is%20one%20of%20my%20personal%20passions%2C%20and%20I%20took%20a%20remote%20consulting%20job%20with%20a%20nonprofit%20biodiversity%20lab%20based%20in%20Zurich%20for%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20of%20my%20trips%20to%20Zurich%2C%20I%20met%20my%20now-cofounder.%20Looking%20for%20a%20cofounder%20in%20the%20months%20prior%20was%20almost%20like%20dating%20%E2%80%94%20finding%20the%20right%20one%20was%20the%20most%20challenging%20part%2C%20and%20now%20that%20I%20have%2C%20it%20feels%20so%20right.%20Together%2C%20we%20incorporated%20biodiversityX%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20tech%20company%20providing%20real-time%20forest%20analytics%2C%20in%20Zurich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELosing%20a%20job%20is%20traumatic%2C%20but%20it's%20humbling%20to%20think%20about%20how%20much%20Google%20transformed%20my%20life.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20good%20place%20to%20grow%20and%20develop%20as%20a%20leader%2C%20and%20I%20miss%20the%20culture%2C%20the%20food%2C%20and%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%2C%20I%20thought%20a%20career%20had%20to%20be%20very%20linear%20%E2%80%94%20one%20promotion%20after%20another%3B%20tomorrow%20needs%20to%20be%20bigger%20than%20yesterday.%20Today%2C%20I%20see%20things%20as%20a%20bit%20more%20fluid%20and%20view%20the%20layoff%20as%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%20Being%20an%20entrepreneur%20%E2%80%94%20the%20degree%20of%20responsibility%20and%20the%20spe