%3Cp%3EThanking%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20AAP%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20from%20Jangpura%2C%20Mr%20Sisodia%20said%20Patparganj%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bheart%20of%20the%20education%20revolution%20in%20Delhi%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Avadh%20Ojha%20joined%20the%20party%2C%20I%20felt%20Patparganj%20would%20be%20the%20best%20seat%20for%20a%20teacher%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20glad%20to%20%26quot%3Bhand%20over%20the%20responsibility%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20am%20now%20ready%20to%20do%20in%20Jangpura%20what%20I%20did%20for%20education%20and%20development%20in%20Patparganj.%20From%20Patparganj%20to%20Jangpura%2C%20my%20pledge%20is%20firm%3A%20to%20make%20Delhi%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraveen%20Kumar%2C%20the%20current%20Jangpura%20MLA%2C%20has%20been%20accommodated%20in%20the%20Janakpuri%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Avadh%20Ojha%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20AAP%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Patparganj%20is%20a%20safe%20seat.%20The%20east%20Delhi%20constituency%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20AAP%20stronghold%20that%20has%20been%20represented%20by%20Mr%20Sisodia%20since%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20none%20of%20the%20sitting%20MLAs%20in%20these%2020%20seats%20have%20been%20repeated%20this%20time.%20AAP%20is%20pushing%20hard%20for%20a%20fourth%20term%20and%20the%20move%20to%20change%20sitting%20MLAs%20appears%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20countering%20anti-incumbency%20or%20complaints%20against%20a%20specific%20legislator%20in%20his%2Fher%20constituency.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20BJP%20chief%20Virendraa%20Sachdeva%20said%20that%20they%20have%20got%20information%20that%20many%20sitting%20AAP%20MLAs%20don't%20want%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%20because%20people%20have%20decided%20to%20vote%20for%20change.%20%26quot%3B(Former)%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20(Sisodia)%20has%20fled%2C%20imagine%20the%20fear.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Atishi%20wil