ent%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-spotted-at-kalina-airport-with-daughter-dua-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F116133468.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-American%20Family%20To%20%26quot%3BPress%20Charges%26quot%3B%20Against%20Woman%20Over%20Racist%20Abuse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian-American%20family%20subjected%20to%20racial%20harassment%20last%20month%20plans%20to%20press%20charges%20against%20the%20woman%20who%20hurled%20abuses%20at%20them%2C%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20accountability%20and%20speaking%20out%20against%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20November%20when%20renowned%20photographer%20Pervez%20Taufiq%2C%2050%2C%20was%20travelling%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20three%20kids%20from%20Mexico%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20in%20a%20bus.%20A%20fellow%20female%20passenger%20went%20on%20a%20racist%20diatribe%20against%20the%20family%20while%20it%20was%20onboard%20the%20United%20Airlines%20shuttle%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaufiq%20posted%20a%20video%20online%20of%20his%20family's%20ordeal%20that%20shows%20the%20woman%20racially%20abusing%20them%2C%20using%20expletives%20and%20making%20derogatory%20gestures%20at%20them.%20%E2%80%9CYour%20family%20is%20from%20India%2C%20you%20have%20no%20respect.%20You%20have%20no%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20woman%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20when%20Taufiq%20says%20he%20is%20an%20American%2C%20the%20woman%20hurls%20back%2C%20using%20an%20expletive%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20American...You%20are%20from...India.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9COur%20thought%20process%20is%20we%20need%20to%20take%20her%20and%20hold%20her%20accountable%20in%20the%20court%20of%20law.%20United%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20was%20not%20able%20to%20help%20us%20with%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taufiq%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20has%20been%20no%20sense%20of%20accountability%20or%20introspection%20forthcoming%20from%20the%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe're%20going%20to%20press%20charges...We're%20heavily%20considering%20pushing%20it%20forward.%20We%20have%20legal%20people%20who%20have%20consulted%20with%20us%20and%20told%20us%20as%20much%20that%20it%20would%20be%20the%20smart%20move%20and%20to%20not%20let%20this%20just%20die%20into%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20generation%20is%20very%20different%20from%20my%20parents'%20generation.%20I%20think%20in%20my%20parents'%20time%2C%20they%20would%20have%20put%20their%20head%20down%2C%20kept%20quiet%2C%20that%20type%20of%20thing.%20I%20think%20those%20times%20are%20over.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20it's%20up%20to%20our%20generation%20to%20really%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20type%20of%20thing%20that%20you%20can%20do%20without%20consequence%2C%26quot%3B%20Taufiq%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20initially%20he%20didn't%20have%20the%20name%20of%20the%20woman%20and%20that%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20any%20legal%20action%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20her%20own%20family%20and%20her%20friends%20have%20come%20forward%20to%20us%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20want%20to%20apologize%20to%20you'...%20%E2%80%98we%20need%20to%20share%20her%20name%20with%20you%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20tell%20you%20what's%20going%20on'.%20That%20was%20enormous%2C%20obviously%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taufiq%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20learnt%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20is%20a%20habit%20in%20her%20hometown%20and%20that%20people%20have%20known%20her%20to%20do%20this%20type%20of%20thing%2C%20and%20she%20has%20this%20type%20of%20behaviour%2C%20even%20her%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20half%20of%20them%2C%20don't%20speak%20to%20her%20anymore%20because%20of%20this%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Arlene%20Consuela%2C%20Taufiq%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20is%20the%20irony%20of%20it%20all%E2%80%9D%20given%20that%20her%20name%20is%20of%20Mexican%20descent.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20one%20immigrant%20is%20basically%20telling%20another%20immigrant%20that%20they%20are%20not%20American.%E2%80%9D%20Taufiq%20said%20his%20eldest%20son%2C%20who%20is%2011%20years%20old%2C%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20business%20class%20cabin%20next%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20asking%20him%20questions%20about%20whether%20his%20family%20was%20from%20India.%20In%20the%20shuttle%20bus%2C%20she%20even%20told%20Taufiq's%20younger%20kids%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshut%20up%E2%80%9D%20as%20they%20were%20talking%20excitedly%20about%20other%20planes%20at%20the%20tarmac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20a%20news%20outlet%2C%20the%20woman%20attributed%20her%20behaviour%20to%20a%20brain%20injury.%20Taufiq%20said%20brain%20injuries%20may%20cause%20speech%20impediments%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20they%20certainly%20don't%20make%20you%20racist%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20Taufiq%20said%20he%20feels%20it%20is%20his%20%E2%80%9Cduty%20and%20responsibility%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20know%20that%2C%20yes%20this%20happens.%20No%2C%20it's%20not%20okay.%20Stand%20up%20for%20yourself%2C%20and%20to%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20fact%20that...%20if%20you're%20on%20the%20bus%20with%20someone%20who's%20being%20racially%20harassed%2C%20a%20family%20that's%20being%20racially%20harassed%2C%20you%20stand%20up.%20You%20say%20something.%E2%80%9D%20He%20voices%20gratitude%20for%20the%20sole%20person%20on%20the%20shuttle%20bus%20who%20stood%20up%20for%20him%20and%20his%20family%20during%20the%20entire%20incident.%20%E2%80%9CI'm%20so%20grateful%20for%20that%20one%20gentleman%20who%20did%20stand%20by%20us.%20But%20I%20really%20wish%20there%20were%20more.%20And%20going%20forward%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20make%20a%20personal%20note%20-%20if%20I%20see%20something%20like%20this%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20personally%20get%20involved.%20I%20won't%20let%20them%20(be)%20isolated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taufiq%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20no%20one%20on%20the%20entire%20bus%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20family%20as%20they%20were%20being%20targeted%20with%20racial%20slurs%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20jarring%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20pretty%20brutal%20to%20have%20nobody.%20And%20the%20silences%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20was%20incredibly%20deafening.%E2%80%9D%20The%20photographer%20said%20anyone%20who%20goes%20through%20or%20is%20going%20through%20an%20incident%20like%20this%2C%20should%20know%20that%20there's%20support%20out%20there%2C%20that%20the%20right%20people%20will%20support%20them%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20so%20many%20of%20us%20would%20stand%20by%20their%20side.%20And%20for%20people%20who%20are%20racist%2C%20I%20think%20they%20should%20learn%20a%20lesson%20from%20this%20as%20well%2C%20that%20maybe%20they're%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20this.%E2%80%9D%20As%20the%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20went%20viral%2C%20Taufiq%20said%20he%20is%20grateful%20for%20the%20outpouring%20of%20support%20that%20he%20and%20his%20family%20have%20received%20on%20and%20off%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20had%20calls%20and%20text%20messages%20from%20people%20in%20China%2C%20France%2C%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20all%20over%20the%20world%20who%20have%20seen%20this%20video...%20and%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98we%20just%20want%20you%20to%20know%20we're%20with%20you.'%20That%20is%20the%20most%20touching%20thing%20that%20could%20ever%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaufiq%2C%20whose%20work%20constantly%20takes%20him%20to%20destinations%20across%20the%20world%2C%20recalled%20that%20on%20a%20United%20flight%20over%20the%20weekend%20from%20New%20York%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Boston%2C%20one%20of%20the%20airline's%20staff%20members%20recognised%20him%2C%20stopped%20him%20and%20said%20%E2%80%98Is%20i