83%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelangana%20MLA%20Holds%20German%20Citizenship%3A%20Centre%20Tells%20High%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Ministry%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20(Mr%20Ramesh's)%20misrepresentation%2Fconcealment%20of%20fact%20misled%20the%20Government%20of%20India...%20Had%20he%20revealed%20he%20had%20not%20resided%20in%20India%20for%20one%20year%20before%20making%20the%20application%2C%20the%20competent%20authority%20in%20this%20ministry%20would%20not%20have%20granted%20citizenship...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20then%20filed%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Home%20Ministry's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20then%20asked%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20disclosing%2C%20and%20enclosing%2C%20details%20related%20to%20the%20surrender%20of%20his%20German%20passport%2C%20and%20also%20proof%20he%20had%20given%20up%20his%20German%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%20the%20then%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20quashed%20the%20bypoll%20victory%20for%20this%20same%20reason.%20Mr%20Ramesh%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20wrangled%20a%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20while%20the%20stay%20was%20in%20effect%2C%20he%20contested%20and%20won%20the%202014%20and%202018%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733731680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fc42rqgv_former-brs-mla-chennamaneni-ramesh_625x300_09_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchennamaneni-ramesh-german-citizen-vemulawada-mla-telangana-high-court-7206451%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ex-BRS%20leader%20Chennamaneni%20Ramesh%20is%20a%20German%20citizen%20and%20used%20forged%20documents%20-%20presenting%20himself%20as%20an%20Indian%20national%20-%20to%20contest%20the%20Vemulawada%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20the%20Telangana%20High%20Court%20ruled%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchennamaneni-ramesh-german-citizen-vemulawada-mla-telangana-high-court-7206451%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20An%20Unstable%20Middle%20East%20Is%20A%20Risk%20For%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fe7frricg_syria-civil-war-reuters_625x300_08_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20dozen%20or%20so%20years%2C%20India%20has%20effectively%20transformed%20its%20%26quot%3BLink%20West%26quot%3B%20policy%20into%20an%20%26quot%3BAct%20West%26quot%3B%20policy.%20The%20transactional%20partnerships%20of%20previous%20decades%20have%20been%20replaced%20by%20a%20comprehensive%2C%20strategic%20relationship%2C%20expanding%2C%20renewing%2C%20and%20reigniting%20the%20intensity%20of%20exchanges%20at%20the%20highest%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20countries%20of%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20(GCC)%20have%20clearly%20become%20a%20central%20focus%2C%20as%20these%20oil-rich%20nations%20have%20not%20only%20sought%20to%20enhance%20historic%20ties%20at%20the%20modern-day%20strategic%20level%20but%20have%20also%20adopted%20their%20own%20%26quot%3BAct%20East%26quot%3B%20policies%2C%20with%20visions%20extending%20to%202023%20and%20even%202040.%20This%20aligns%20with%20India's%20goal%20of%20achieving%20a%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Bharat%26quot%3B%20by%202047.%20The%20blending%20of%20synergies%20and%20converging%20mutual%20interests%20has%20become%20the%20underlying%20theme%20of%20interactions.%20High-level%20committees%20have%20been%20established%20to%20monitor%20progress%20across%20all%20areas%20of%20individual%20relationships%2C%20often%20following%20the%20visits%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20many%20of%20these%20countries.%20Several%20of%20these%20countries%20have%20hosted%20him%20multiple%20times%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20further%20strengthening%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%2C%20with%20six%20visits%2C%20stands%20out%20and%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20India's%20third-largest%20trading%20partner.%20Sheikh%20Zayed%20has%20visited%20India%20four%20times%2C%20including%20as%20the%20Chief%20Guest%20on%20Republic%20Day%20and%20for%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Other%20leaders%20have%20shown%20a%20similar%20interest%20in%20India's%20opportunities%2C%20as%20they%20follow%20their%20own%20brand%20of%20strategic%20autonomy%20in%20an%20increasingly%20fractured%20world.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20also%20become%20perhaps%20the%20first%20Indian%20leader%20to%20receive%20the%20highest%20honours%20from%20these%20nations%2C%20which%20is%20further%20testament%20to%20the%20importance%20they%20place%20on%20their%20relationship%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20More%20Shy%20Of%20Multilateral%20Frameworks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20often%20criticised%20for%20lacking%20a%20strategic%20vision%20towards%20her%20extended%20neighbourhood%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20to%20her%20own%20security%20and%20stability.%20Historically%2C%20relationships%20were%20mostly%20dealt%20with%20in%20a%20bilateral%20framework%20of%20cooperation%2C%20often%20with%20limited%20objectives.%20While%20this%20continues%2C%20recent%20years%20have%20seen%20a%20renewed%20focus%20on%20broader%20trilateral%2C%20quadrilateral%2C%20multilateral%2C%20sub-regional%2C%20and%20regional%20formats%2C%20such%20as%20the%20I2U2%20(India%2C%20USA%2C%20UAE%2C%20and%20Israel)%2C%20IUSU%20(India%2C%20UAE%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20USA)%2C%20India-GCC%2C%20IMEEC%20(India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20participation%20in%20G20%20and%20COP%20mechanisms%2C%20particularly%20those%20held%20in%20Egypt%20and%20the%20UAE.%20The%20BRICS%20and%20the%20SCO%20are%20other%20groupings%20in%20which%20several%20Middle%20Eastern%20countries%20have%20either%20become%20members%20or%20dialogue%20partners%2C%20further%20expanding%20the%20framework%20of%20cooperation%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ongoing%2014-month-long%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20along%20with%20escalating%20conflicts%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rise%20of%20non-state%20actors%2C%20have%20raised%20the%20spectre%20of%20instability%2C%20volatility%2C%20and%20escalation.%20This%20will%20directly%20impact%20energy%20security%2C%20food%20security%2C%20economic%20engagement%2C%20maritime%20connectivity%2C%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%2010%20million%20Indian%20expatriates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20region%20is%20concerned%2C%20and%20so%20is%20India%2C%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20The%20involvement%20of%20major%20powers%20appears%20to%20be%20at%20its%20lowest%20point%2C%20with%20their%20capacity%20to%20prevent%20wars%20or%20effectively%20intervene%20to%20reduce%20intensity%20or%20expansion%20scarce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20be%20due%20to%20short-sighted%20geopolitical%20manoeuvres.%20However%2C%20the%20costs%20will%20be%20high%20if%20a%20real%20escalation%20occurs.%20For%20New%20Delhi%2C%20nascent%20sub-regional%20and%20regional%20mechanisms%20are%20being%20adversely%20impacted%2C%20some%20even%20before%20they%20have%20fully%20taken%20off%E2%80%94such%20as%20the%20IMEEC%E2%80%94though%20India%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20are%20continuing%20their%20work%20and%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20address%20various%20bilateral%20and%20regional%20projects%20and%20issues%2C%20recent%20engagements%20are%20noteworthy.%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20is%20touring%20Qatar%20and%20Bahrain%20from%20December%206-9%20for%20the%20Doha%20Forum%20and%20to%20co-chair%20the%20fourth%20India-Bahrain%20High-Level%20Joint%20Commission.%20Qatar%20has%20become%20a%20key%20player%20in%20international%20negotiations%2C%20notably%20playing%20a%20central%20role%20in%20ceasefire%20efforts%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20Consequently%2C%20foreign%20ministers%20from%20Turkey%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20Russia%20were%20expected%20to%20meet%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Doha%20Forum%20for%20urgent%20discussions%20on%20Syria.%20During%20his%20visit%2C%20Jaishankar%20will%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20his%20counterparts%20and%20leaders%20from%20Qatar%20and%20other%20countries%20at%20this%20critical%20juncture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20following%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20Kuwaiti%20Foreign%20Minister%20Abdullah%20Ali%20Al%20Yahya%20led%20a%20delegation%20to%20India%20from%20December%203-4%20to%20discuss%20bilateral%20and%20regional%20issues.%20The%20Joint%20Commission%20has%20been%20upgraded%20to%20the%20ministerial%20level%2C%20and%20several%20Joint%20Working%20Groups%20will%20be%20established%20to%20address%20various%20dimensions%20of%20the%20comprehensive%20relationship.%20A%20visit%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20to%20Kuwait%20is%20also%20being%20discussed%2C%20which%20could%20not%20take%20place%20earlier%20due%20to%20scheduling%20issues.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSimilarly%2C%20the%2013th%20round%20of%20Foreign%20Office%20Consultations%20was%20held%20with%20Egypt%20on%20December%205.%20The%2013th%20round%20of%20the%20India-Oman%20Strategic%20Consultative%20Group%20(IOSCG)%20meeting%20also%20took%20place%20on%20December%203%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%94both%20at%20the%20Secretary%20level.%20During%20these%20meetings%2C%20bilateral%20and%20regional%20issues%20were%20discussed%20in%20detail.%20India%20and%20Syria%20also%20held%20the%206th%20round%20of%20Foreign%20Office%20consultations%20on%20November%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20Frequent%20Meetings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20during%20his%2010th%20visit%2C%20Jaishankar%20met%20with%20his%20counterpart%2C%20Abdullah%20Bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20of%20the%20UAE.%20They%20reviewed%20the%20entire%20spectrum%20of%20the%20comprehensive%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20and%20the%20EAM%20expressed%20satisfaction%20over%20the%20continued%20exchange%20of%20high-level%20visits%20and%20the%20exponential%20growth%20of%20the%20relationship.%20They%20also%20discussed%20regional%20and%20global%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest%2C%20which%20included%20a%20deeper%20discussion%20of%20the%20evolving%20situation%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20discussions%20with%20another%20major%20strategic%20partner%2C%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20talks%20were%20held%20during%20the%20visit%20of%20Prince%20Faisal%20bin%20Farhan%20Al%20Saud%2C%20the%20Saudi%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20to%20New%20Delhi%20on%20November%2012-13.%20During%20the%20meeting%2C%20both%20sides%20discussed%20avenues%20to%20strengthen%20the%20strategic%20partnership%20between%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20in%20areas%20including%20trade%2C%20investment%2C%20energy%2C%20defence%2C%20security%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20consular%20matters.%20Both%20Foreign%20Ministers%20also%20exchanged%20views%20on%20regional%20and%20international%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest%20at%20the%20second%20ministerial%20meeting%20of%20the%20Political%2C%20Security%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Cultural%20Committee%20(PSSC)%20of%20the%20India-Saudi%20Arabia%20Strategic%20Partnership%20Council%20(SPC).%3Cbr%3E%5CnPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20met%20Iranian%20President%20Dr.%20Pezeshkian%20in%20Kazan%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20Summit.%20He%20urged%20all%20sides%20to%20exercise%20restraint%20and%20prioritize%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%2C%20while%20India%20continued%20to%20provide%20humanitarian%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20frequency%20of%20these%20high-level%20interactions%20in%20less%20than%20two%20months%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20regional%20stability%20and%20security%2C%20and%20India's%20commitment%20to%20this%20cause.%20The%20Indian%20Navy%20is%20already%20in%20the%20region%20ensuring%20the%20security%20of%20merchant%20shipping%20and%20maritime%20routes.%20But%20the%20region%20remains%20a%20powder%20keg%2C%20with%20numerous%20active%20conflicts%2C%20hotspots%2C%20and%20geopolitical%20fault%20lines%20that%20could%20become%20even%20more%20dangerous%20unless%20pragmatic%20approaches%20are%20adopted%20by%20major%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20India's%20former%20Ambassador%20to%20Jordan%2C%20Libya%20and%20Malta)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733731680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fe7frricg_syria-civil-war-reuters_625x300_08_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-an-unstable-middle-east-is-a-risk-for-india-too-7206321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20volatility%20in%20Middle%20East%20will%20directly%20impact%20energy%20security%2C%20food%20security%2C%20economic%20engagement%2C%20maritime%20connectivity%2C%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%2010%20million%20Indian%20expatriates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-an-unstable-middle-east-is-a-risk-for-india-too-7206321%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20picks%20lawyer%20Alina%20Habba%20as%20counsellor%20to%20US%20president%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733731083000%2