20sati%20had%20been%20abolished%20in%20Hinduism%2C%20the%20Muslim%20community%20continues%20to%20permit%20the%20practice%20of%20having%20multiple%20wives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20claim%20the%20right%20to%20have%20four%20wives%2C%20perform%20Halala%2C%20or%20practice%20Triple%20Talaq...%20UCC%20isn't%20something%20that%20VHP%2C%20RSS%2C%20or%20Hinduism%20advocates.%20The%20country's%20top%20court%20also%20talks%20about%20it...%20I%20am%20taking%20an%20oath%20that%20this%20country%20will%20definitely%20bring%20a%20single%20law%2C%20and%20it%20will%20bring%20it%20very%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733727840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpd3r8jo8_asaduddin-owaisi_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasaduddin-owaisi-justice-shekhar-yadav-high-court-judge-says-law-works-according-to-majority-a-owaisi-reacts-7206000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20judge's%20remarks%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Visva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20have%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%2C%20with%20AIMIM%20leader%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20questioning%20how%20a%20minority%20party%20can%20expect%20justice%20from%20such%20a%20judge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasaduddin-owaisi-justice-shekhar-yadav-high-court-judge-says-law-works-according-to-majority-a-owaisi-reacts-7206000%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Pushpa%202%3A%20The%20Rule%20off%20to%20a%20slow%20start%20on%20Monday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733727838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116128499%2Cimgsize-55092.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fpushpa-2-the-rule-box-office-collection-day-5-upda