r%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20offers%20everything%20from%20access%20to%20data%20centers%20to%20GPU%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20got%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%20memo%20the%20startup%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENscale%2C%20a%20London-based%20startup%20providing%20companies%20with%20access%20to%20data%20centers%20and%20clusters%20of%20AI%20chips%2C%20has%20raised%20%24155%20million%20in%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%2C%20which%20came%20out%20of%20stealth%20in%20May%202024%2C%20bills%20itself%20as%20a%20fully%20integrated%20AI%20infrastructure%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20hyperscaler%2C%20Nscale%20provides%20the%20%26quot%3Bfull%20stack%26quot%3B%20of%20technologies%20companies%20need%20to%20train%20and%20run%20AI%20applications%20like%20large%20language%20models.%20That%20includes%20data%20centers%2C%20software%2C%20and%20graphics%20processing%20units%2C%20Nscale's%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Joshua%20Payne%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20differentiates%20itself%20from%20AI%20cloud%20providers%2C%20such%20as%20Lambda%20Labs%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fcoreweave-closes-650-mln-secondary-sale-ai-startups-lure-investors-2024-11-13%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoreweave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20offer%20only%20specific%20components%2C%20such%20as%20GPUs%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-ai-infrastructure-data-center-microsoft-blackrock-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20infrastructure%20layer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20providing%20everything%20from%20its%20own%20data%20centers%20to%20virtualized%20GPU%20nodes%2C%20Payne%20said%20that%20the%20company%20could%20leverage%20better%20unit%20economics%20than%20its%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20for%20the%20industry%20is%20chicken%20and%20egg.%20Take%20an%20LLM%20customer%20%E2%80%94%20they%20may%20want%2010%2C000%20GPUs%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20expertise%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20our%20competitors%20don't%20own%20their%20own%20data%20centers%2C%20so%20they%20have%20to%20license%20them.%20In%20our%20case%2C%20we%20have%20all%20of%20that%20in-house.%20Given%20that%20we%20are%20able%20to%20own%20all%20those%20segments%20in%20the%20value%20chain%2C%20we're%20faster%20and%20cheaper.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPayne%20said%20that%20Nscale%20pivoted%20to%20focus%20on%20AI%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20full%20stack%20after%20the%20public%20release%20of%20ChatGPT-3.%20%26quot%3BSo%20our%20thesis%20was%2C%20if%20this%20is%20indeed%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution%20as%20people%20are%20claiming%2C%20then%20how%20would%20you%20build%20a%20resilient%20AI%20cloud%20that%20would%20survive%20commodity%20cycles%3F%20said%20Payne.%20%26quot%3BWe%20found%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20that%20was%20to%20vertically%20integrate%20it%2C%20building%20both%20data%20centers%2C%20GPUs%2C%20and%20software.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20emerged%20from%20stealth%2C%20it%20has%20rapidly%20grown%20its%20pipeline%20of%20greenfield%20data%20center%20capacity%20across%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%20from%20300%20megawatts%20to%201.3%20gigawatts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20makes%20its%20money%20by%20building%20data%20centers%2C%20purchasing%20GPUs%2C%20and%20deploying%20AI%20cloud%20services%2C%20which%20it%20then%20leases%20on%20an%20hourly%20basis.%20Clients%20can%20sign%20contracts%20for%20any%20given%20period%20of%20time%20to%20use%20the%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandton%20Capital%20Partners%20led%20the%20%24155%20million%20round%2C%20which%20also%20included%20participation%20from%20Kestrel%2C%20Bluesky%20Asset%20Management%2C%20and%20Florence%20Capital.%20The%20startup%20previously%20raised%20more%20than%20%2430%20million