%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818.jpg%20773w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386775%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENaseema%20is%20a%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20a%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20(NHRC)%20advisory%20group%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constant%20fear%20of%20the%20police%2C%20the%20forced%20hiding%2C%20and%20the%20need%20to%20constantly%20run%20were%20not%20just%20external%20pressures%3B%20they%20profoundly%20shaped%20her%20self-perception%20and%20her%20struggle%20to%20define%20her%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20hard%20to%20define%20yourself%20as%20a%20daughter%20of%20a%20red-light%20area%20and%20not%20a%20sex%20worker.%20This%20is%20a%20concept%20that%20is%20unheard%20of%20to%20the%20outside%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20But%20Naseema%20never%20let%20go%20of%20her%20desire%20to%20define%20herself%20beyond%20what%20the%20world%20forced%20on%20her.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20a%20small%20vegetable%20stall%20that%20he%20pushes%20around%20on%20the%20road%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20want%20their%20child%20to%20continue%20doing%20the%20same%20work%20they%20do%2C%20a%20sex%20worker%20also%20does%20not%20want%20their%20child%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20She%20wants%20better%20for%20her%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naseema%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20always%20so%20scared%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201995%2C%20when%20Naseema%20was%20a%20young%20teen%2C%20IAS%20Rajbala%20Verma%2C%20who%20was%20posted%20as%20a%20district%20magistrate%2C%20started%20some%20programmes%20to%20help%20sex%20workers%20in%20the%20area%20learn%20skills%2C%20such%20as%20embroidery%2C%20and%20get%20access%20to%20healthcare.%20Naseema%20took%20part%20in%20one%20such%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Better%20Life%20Option%E2%80%99.%20She%20had%20already%20learnt%20embroidery%20from%20her%20mother%2C%20was%20skilled%20at%20it%2C%20and%20stood%20out.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20she%20struggled%20with%20the%20anxiety%20of%20having%20to%20answer%20certain%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20so%20scared%20that%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20speak.%20Because%20what%20if%20that%20conversation%20leads%20to%20them%20asking%20me%20where%20I%E2%80%99m%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%2013%20years%20old%2C%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20school%20and%20move%20to%20Sitamarhi%20to%20live%20with%20her%20maternal%20grandmother.%20However%2C%20by%20this%20time%2C%20she%20had%20already%20resolved%20to%20build%20a%20life%20for%20herself%2C%20one%20that%20would%20need%20no%20hiding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20heard%20about%20an%20organisation%20there%20that%20was%20helping%20adolescent%20girls.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20they%20did%20or%20how%20they%20could%20help.%20I%20was%20sure%20that%20if%20I%20just%20tried%20a%20little%2C%20I%20could%20figure%20my%20life%20out%20and%20make%20something%20of%20myself.%20So%2C%20I%20locked%20myself%20in%20a%20room%20for%20days%2C%20refused%20to%20eat%20or%20speak%20to%20anybody%2C%20until%20I%20was%20taken%20to%20where%20that%20organisation%20was%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20kept%20asking%20why%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20there%2C%20and%20I%20would%20say%20that%20there%20is%20a%20friend%20that%20I%20really%20want%20to%20meet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20chuckles.%20Her%20persistence%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20one%20day%20she%20met%20with%20the%20people%20from%20%E2%80%98Adithi%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20works%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255139%2Fmumbai-designer-covid19-underprivileged-women-earn-money-donation-livelihood-fashion-cloth-bags-scrunchies-gurmeen-shrivastav-srujna-ngo-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20women%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20very%20next%20day%2C%20Adithi%20workers%20came%20to%20her%20house%20and%20urged%20her%20father%20to%20let%20her%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20organisation%20where%20she%20would%20learn%20valuable%20skills%20and%20turn%20her%20life%20around.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20stunned%20when%20they%20came%20to%20our%20house.%20It%20was%20like%20my%20legs%20had%20become%20jelly%20and%20the%20cola%20that%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20serve%20them%2C%20wound%20up%20on%20their%20clothes.%20I%20laugh%20as%20I%20say%20that%20now%2C%20but%20that%20day%20I%20could%20have%20died%20of%20relief%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20worked%20with%20the%20organisation%20till%202002%2C%20becoming%20a%20skilled%20micro-level%20planner%20and%20trainer.%20Her%20years%20in%20Sitamarhi%20with%20Adithi%20taught%20her%20about%20the%20law%2C%20child%20rights%2C%20and%20the%20safety%20the%20Constitution%20grants%20each%20and%20every%20citizen%20of%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Jugnu%E2%80%99%3A%20Where%20children%20express%20their%20dreams%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Naseema%20came%20back%20to%20Muzaffarpur%20in%202002%2C%20she%20saw%20the%20issues%20plaguing%20her%20home%20town%20with%20a%20renewed%20sense%20of%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20raid%20in%20the%20area%20right%20next%20to%20us%2C%20women%20were%20arrested%20and%20taken%20away%20without%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20female%20constable%20because%20those%20rules%2C%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20do%20not%20apply%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20next%20day%2C%20I%20sat%20at%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20tea%20stall%2C%20watching%20as%20the%20police%20rounded%20up%20people%20from%20the%20area.%20A%20meeting%20was%20taking%20place%2C%20led%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98Samaj%20Sudhar%20Committee%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20they%20told%20the%20women%20they%20could%20learn%20skills%20like%20tailoring%2C%20embroidery%2C%20and%20other%20jobs%20offered%20by%20government%20schemes.%20When%20the%20women%20asked%20when%20they%20could%20start%20working%20and%20how%20soon%20they%20would%20get%20the%20money%2C%20they%20were%20told%20it%20would%20take%20six%20months%20to%20set%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20asked%20how%20they%20could%20earn%20a%20living%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20committee%20took%20it%20as%20an%20insult.%20As%20if%20we%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20ask%20questions%20that%20dictate%20whether%20we%20get%20to%20eat%20two%20meals%20a%20day%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENaseema%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20children%20in%20the%20community.%20When%20the%20woman%2C%20often%20the%20primary%20breadwinner%2C%20is%20arrested%2C%20who%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20family%3F%20The%20dependents%2C%20especially%20the%20children%2C%20are%20left%20to%20suffer.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20young%20girl%20in%20the%20household%2C%20what%20options%20does%20she%20have%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseema%E2%80%99s%20work%20with%20Adithi%2C%20along%20with%20her%20increasing%20involvement%20in%20community%20issues%2C%20led%20her%20to%20start%20a%20community-based%20organisation%20called%20%E2%80%98Parcham%E2%80%99%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%98flag%E2%80%99%20in%20Hindi.%20Parcham%20was%20not%20an%20NGO%3B%20it%20was%20a%20grassroots%20organisation%20built%20by%20the%20people%20of%20the%20community%2C%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu-1733397844.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jugu%20magazine%20cover%20art%2C%20written%20and%20designed%20by%20hand%20with%20elements%20such%20as%20drums%2C%20camels%2C%20a%20veil%20clad%20woman%2C%20and%20musical%20instruments.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu-1733397844.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu-1733397844-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl